76
00:04:18,310 --> 00:04:19,571
into the actors in your game,

77
00:04:19,772 --> 00:04:21,253
which generates emergent gameplay,

78
00:04:21,313 --> 00:04:23,455
which is then viewed as emergent storytelling.

79
00:04:24,616 --> 00:04:27,921
